sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User <<user interaction>>
    participant Filter as JwtAuthenticationFilter <<security>>
    participant Controller as WorkshopTemplateController <<coordinator>>
    participant Service as WorkshopTemplateService <<service>>
    participant Spec as WorkshopTemplateSpecification <<service>>
    participant Repo as WorkshopTemplateRepository <<entity>>
    participant DB as DB

    User->>Filter: 1. GET /api/workshops/templates/filter?keyword=...&status=...&...
    activate Filter

    Filter->>Filter: 2. Extract JWT from Authorization header
    Filter->>Filter: 3. Validate token and set SecurityContext

    alt 3A: Token invalid or missing
        Filter-->>User: 3A1. 401 Unauthorized
    else 3B: Token valid
        Filter->>Controller: 3B1. Forward request with authenticated context
        deactivate Filter
        activate Controller

        Controller->>Service: 4. searchWorkshopTemplates(keyword, name, status, vendorId, tagId, minPrice, maxPrice, minDuration, maxDuration, minRating)
        activate Service

        Service->>Service: 5. Build base Specification (conjunction — match all)

        Service->>Spec: 6. Conditionally add filter specifications
        activate Spec
        Note right of Spec: For each non-null param:<br/>keyword → searchByKeyword()<br/>name → hasName()<br/>status → hasStatus()<br/>vendorId → hasVendorId()<br/>tagId → hasTagId()<br/>price → hasPriceBetween()<br/>duration → hasDurationBetween()<br/>rating → hasMinRating()
        Spec-->>Service: 6A. Combined Specification<WorkshopTemplate>
        deactivate Spec

        Service->>Repo: 7. findAll(spec)
        activate Repo
        Repo->>DB: 8. SELECT with dynamic criteria (JPA Criteria API)
        activate DB
        DB-->>Repo: 8A. List of matching WorkshopTemplate entities
        deactivate DB
        Repo-->>Service: 7A. List<WorkshopTemplate>
        deactivate Repo

        Service->>Service: 9. Map each template → WorkshopTemplateResponse via mapToResponse()
        Note right of Service: For each template:<br/>- Extract tags from workshopTags<br/>- Map images to WorkshopImageResponse<br/>- Map tags to WTagResponse<br/>- Build WorkshopTemplateResponse

        Service-->>Controller: 9A. List<WorkshopTemplateResponse>
        deactivate Service

        Controller-->>User: 10. 200 OK — ApiResponse.success("Workshop templates filtered successfully", list)
        deactivate Controller
    end
